import React from 'react';
import { PortHead } from './components/header';
import {
	Main,
	Place,
	Tall,
	StaTall,
	StaLand,
	Flex,
	Land,
	Spacer,
	BoxT,
	StaLandV,
} from './components/components';
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom';

export const Portfolio = () => (
	<main>
		<PortHead />
		<Spacer h="h4" />
		<Main>
			<Land
				to="/progetti/yape"
				container="w-70 center w-100-m"
				article="dim"
				background="./img/lima/4.png"
				title="Metro de Lima"
				group="segnaletica"
			/>
			<Spacer h="h4 h3-m" />

			<StaLandV
				container="center w-80 w-100-m"
				background="./img/ducati.mp4"
				title="Sempre più a contatto con la tua Ducati"
				group="video • "
			/>
			<Spacer h="h4 h3-m" />
			<BoxT title="posters">
				<Flex class="justify-between" width="w-100">
					<StaTall
						container="w-third mt4 mt1-m"
						background="./img/mourn.png"
					/>
					<StaTall
						container="w-third mt4 mt1-m mh3 mh1-m"
						background="./img/nasa.jpg"
					/>
					<StaTall
						container="w-third mt4 mt1-m "
						background="./img/nasa.jpg"
					/>
				</Flex>
			</BoxT>
		</Main>
	</main>
);
